COMPARA: MACRO &A, &B
         LOAD &A
         SUB &B
         JMPZ IGUAIS
         ENDMACRO

PROCESSA: MACRO &X
          ADD UM
          STORE &X
          ENDMACRO

START: INPUT VAL1
       INPUT VAL2
TESTE: COMPARA VAL1, VAL2
LOOP:  PROCESSA VAL1
       OUTPUT VAL1
       JMP FIM
IGUAIS: OUTPUT ZERO
FIM:    STOP
VAL1: SPACE
VAL2: SPACE
UM: SPACE 1
ZERO: SPACE
